metadata.name: If You Can Make it Here
metadata.description:
Walking the streets of New York, I happened to look up and saw the perfect scene. All the lights, lines of cars and tall building, this view grabbed me. I hope you can find the same excitement in it as I did. 

With all the chaos surrounding us on a daily basis, sometimes you just need to stop, take a deep breath and shoot your shot (even if it's mid-crosswalk) because you definitely don't want to miss it.
